{"tid":2217580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【香港航空】港航推兼職機組人員計劃，變相減薪3成","createTime":"2020-09-25T14:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T17:06:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"998c0bdd42c12ca301f9d079b57121640bc74b9e","tid":2217580,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2762678/【香港航空】港航推兼職機組人員計劃%E3%80%80變相減薪3成（第二版）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2762678%2F%E3%80%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E3%80%91%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E6%8E%A8%E5%85%BC%E8%81%B7%E6%A9%9F%E7%B5%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%25E3%2580%2580%E8%AE%8A%E7%9B%B8%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA3%E6%88%90%EF%BC%88%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=20663e3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2762678/【香港航空】港航推兼職機組人員計劃%E3%80%80變相減薪3成（第二版）</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2762678/250920_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2762678%2F250920_1024.jpg&h=ca98d0d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早於2月已裁員的香港航空（Hong Kong Airlines）繼向機師提出減薪及無薪假計劃，擬再推出兼職機組人員計劃。香港航空回覆本報查詢，確認有關安排，稱為應對2020年11月至2021年2月空中服務員的過剩情況，推出臨時兼職計劃，安排空中服務員在這期間執勤兩個月及休班兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n港航指，參加計劃的空中服務員期間的基本收入和固定津貼將減少30%，而非固定津貼則不會受到影響，他們經公司批准後更可尋找外面的工作機會。港航又指，會密切關注情況，因應狀況調整或取消此計劃。<br />\n<br />\n據香港航空的內部信指，由於預期未來數月運營機數大減，機組人員求下降，推出兼職機組人員計劃，以減少未來4個月的總薪金成本及維持就業。參與員工將於今年11月1日至明年2月28日的其中兩個月轉為兼職，意味基本工資及固定津貼減少3成，料涉約1200名員工。<br />\n<br />\n信件又指，參與計劃的機艙服務員底薪將由7800港元減至約5460港元，參加者分為兩組，分別於今年11月及12月、明年1月及2月工作，期間員工可以找其他兼職，但要向公司申報並獲批准。<br />\n<br />\n99.5%機師參加減薪及無薪假計劃<br />\n<br />\n港航早前向機師及副機師提出無薪假計劃，由10月1日至明年3月31日，維時半年，期間機長及副機長每月的固定收入和津貼將減少60%，已有99.5%機師同意參加延長的無薪假計劃。<br />\n<br />\n港航亦表明已申請了政府第二期的「保就業」計劃，進一步減輕業務負擔。"},{"pid":"fbec5dfa3327e5ac7b17b2abdadf8a8973ecdc46","tid":2217580,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2750000/2752752/20200915_hx_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2750000%2F2752752%2F20200915_hx_1024.jpg&h=c299cc4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港航空在首輪「保就業」計劃中，獲批工資津貼<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">7,712萬元</span></span></strong>，承諾僱員人數2,940人。港航旗下香港航空訓練中心有限公司獲16.2萬元工資津貼，承諾僱員人數6人。"},{"pid":"2ed04486675b43acb3fc02cff95ec513db901863","tid":2217580,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"得份底薪仲要扣錢"},{"pid":"998cc94b1f59260ea13585ffe409c8997fe84dba","tid":2217580,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:26:34.000Z","msg":"出面有撚兼職，做雞鴨定KOL？"},{"pid":"5ba8ac84f0a5b26df184dab6951c70cf0a435af9","tid":2217580,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2230000/2234960/0_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2230000%2F2234960%2F0_1024.jpg&h=94828722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef57b2fbae96a5be6dc7a8e422f5a3c825cd63fc","tid":2217580,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"998cc94b1f59260ea13585ffe409c8997fe84dba","tid":2217580,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14